                  </entry>
               </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">LED(s) not illuminated</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the status and connection of the power supply.</sli>
                     </sl>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">Canâ€™t connect with a PC to the gateway.</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the correct cable (straight Ethernet cable (RJ45 connection))
is used.</sli>
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the Ethernet link 1 &amp; 2 LEDs (<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">LA1</b> &amp; <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">LA2</b>), see <xref href="AB900x_LEDs_CPT_0000588219.dita"
                                 scope="local"
                                 type="concept"
                                 class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                     </sl>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph class="- topic/ph ">No Modbus TCP/IP communication from the NMC.</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the status of the analog and digital transactions in the
live list (Byte 8).</sli>
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the status of the NMC card.</sli>
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the correct cable (straight Ethernet cable (RJ45 connection))
is used.</sli>
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the Modbus-TCP status LED (<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">MTCP</b>), see <xref href="AB900x_LEDs_CPT_0000588219.dita"
                                 scope="local"
                                 type="concept"
                                 class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the IP configuration is correct in the gateway.</sli>
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the Modbus-TCP port configuration in the gateway.</sli>
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the cable is connected to correct Modbus-TCP port
on the gateway, see <xref href="AB900x_Ports_CPT_0000588218.dita"
                                 scope="local"
                                 type="concept"
                                 class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                     </sl>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ph otherprops="AB9001" class="- topic/ph ">No ProfibusDP communication</ph>
                     <ph otherprops="AB9006" class="- topic/ph ">No Ethernet/IP communication</ph>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                        <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the Modbus TCP/IP communication from the NMC.</sli>
                        <sli otherprops="AB9001" class="- topic/sli ">Check the Profibus DP-V1 Network Status LED
(<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">OP</b>), see <xref href="AB900x_LEDs_CPT_0000588219.dita"
                                 scope="local"
                                 type="concept"
                                 class="- topic/xref "/>. </sli>
                        <sli otherprops="AB9006" class="- topic/sli ">Check the EtherNet/IP Network Status LED
(<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">NS</b>), see <xref href="AB900x_LEDs_CPT_0000588219.dita"
                                 scope="local"
                                 type="concept"
                                 class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                     </sl>
                  </entry>
